Extract Variables

date <- as.Date(data$date)
cpi <- data$cpi
log.cpi <- log(cpi)
inflation <- c(NA, diff(log.cpi))

Average Inflation

Estimate

xbar <- mean(inflation, na.rm=TRUE)
print(xbar)
[1] 0.002930255

Standard Error (?)

n <- sum(!is.na(inflation))
s <- sd(inflation, na.rm=TRUE)
se <- s / sqrt(n)
print(se)
[1] 0.0001225183

95% Confidence Interval (?)

xbar + c(-1,1) * 1.96 * se
[1] 0.002690119 0.003170391

Time Series Plot

plot(date, inflation, type="l", col=2)
